fileChanges.details:
Add rules: (1) .archive-preset-pill should have cursor:default instead of cursor:pointer. (2) Override the hover gradient: .archive .archive-preset-filters .archive-preset-pill should NOT have the transition or background gradient properties. (3) Remove any hover state changes. The pills should maintain the same base visual style (border, rounded-full, padding, text size) but without interactive affordances. Suggested CSS:

.archive .archive-preset-filters .archive-preset-pill {
  cursor: default;
  transition: none;
  background: transparent;
}

.archive .archive-preset-filters .archive-preset-pill:hover {
  background: transparent;
  border-color: currentColor;
  color: inherit;
}
